QuestData.Title: Deeds Left Undone
QuestData.Description: In his haste, Ga'nar advanced before this area was secured. He is a matchless warrior, mind you, but his tactics are sometimes costly.$b$bGol'kosh and his troops were ordered to destroy enemy supplies, but ogres have stolen the oil he needs.$b$bRetrieve the oil and see that their mission is carried out, traveler. Then, if they still live, direct them to rejoin me at the citadel's entrance.$b$bI must see my wounded brothers to safety.
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect barrels of Frostwolf Oil and deliver it to Gol'kosh in the supply room.
QuestData.RewardText: Gol'kosh has completed his mission, then.
